"     Lee-may Chen, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?31/6/31849/contributors\">",
"     Jonathan S Berek, MD, MMS",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
